Sentencas: Nickel oxide was introduced as a grain growth inhibitor into Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) electrode to increase its activity for oxygen reduction reaction.
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor

Sentencas: Small amount of NiO can effectively suppress the grain growth of BSCF by spinning the grain boundary and thus increase the electrode surface area, while the particle connection is not obviously affected.
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectra of symmetric cells indicate that the electrode activity for oxygen reduction is indeed effectively improved by introducing NiO additive.
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor

Sentencas: At 600 C, area specific resistance of BSCF+5wt.% NiO is about 36.5% lower than that of pure BSCF electrode.
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor

Sentencas: Single cell tests also demonstrate an improved cell power output by introducing NiO additive.
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor

Sentencas: It implies that the adoption of a sintering inhibitor may be a facile and practical way to increase electrode activity for oxygen reduction, (C) 2011
Titulo: A new way to increase performance of oxide electrode for oxygen reduction using grain growth inhibitor
